title: Set User-Agent om Gravatar requests (fixes #5)
message:
Set User-Agent om Gravatar requests (fixes #5)

We get 403 from Gravatar if we don't send a User-Agent header, any
value will do.

References
https://coderwall.com/p/kgmr9a/gravatar-api-403-response
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/28520689/gravatar-json-profile-request-403-forbidden
